    <string name="helpText"><h1><b><u>Welcome to your habit tracker!</u></b></h1>\n\n
        <b>Interested in how milestones work?</b>\n
        Once you reach 5, 10, 15, 25, 50, and 100 habit events, you will see a message in your
        corresponding habit! (under "View") After you pass 100 habits, you will see a milestone
        for every 50 more habit events that you complete.\n\n
        <b>Interested in how streaks work?</b>\n
        Once you complete your habit 5 times on your specified frequency, you can see your streak
        calculated when you view your habit. Plus, if you forget to enter your habit event, a notification
        will occur at 4pm that day as a reminder!\n\n</string>

